description:
Details: This is a handmade installer of a full modded client for FreeSpace 2 and it does not get any better than that. At the moment, if you want to mod your client, you have to do everything manually. In this package, everything has been done for you. Furthermore, you do not need to have FreeSpace 2 already installed. This is a FULL release, not a patch. What you get is improved lightning, textures, models, sounds, music and screen resolution. An uninstaller is packed too and so is the official manual, reference card, readme file. Note that this has been built off the GOG version of the game. Good luck and god speed!
